<i>noun</i>: 의붓어머니 [의ː부더머니], 새엄마 [새엄마], 새어머니 [새어머니], 계모 [계ː모/게ː모] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>의붓어머니 [의ː부더머니]</dt><br>
<dd>stepmother</dd><br>
<dd>아버지가 재혼하면서 새로 생긴 어머니.</dd><br>
<dd>A woman who becomes one's new mother by marrying one's father.</dd><br>
<dt>새엄마 [새엄마]</dt><br>
<dd>stepmother</dd><br>
<dd>(어린아이의 말로) 새어머니를 이르거나 부르는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>(children's term) A word used to refer to or address one's stepmother.</dd><br>
<dt>새어머니 [새어머니]</dt><br>
<dd>stepmother</dd><br>
<dd>아버지가 새로 맞이한 아내를 이르거나 부르는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to refer to or address the new wife of one's father.</dd><br>
<dt>계모 [계ː모/게ː모]</dt><br>
<dd>stepmother</dd><br>
<dd>아버지가 새로 결혼해서 생긴 어머니.</dd><br>
<dd>A woman who became a mother by marrying a man with a child or children.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>